WEBVTT

00:02.294 --> 00:04.230
I thought it might be nice to get out there
and get to know each other.

00:04.254 --> 00:05.440
I think
what you really mean is

00:05.464 --> 00:07.797
you'd like to impress
the new managing partner.

00:07.883 --> 00:09.360
- And what if I did?
- You wanna impress me?

00:09.384 --> 00:11.046
Do it with a big, fat client.

00:11.136 --> 00:14.004
Zane promised Samantha
she'd be the next name partner.

00:14.097 --> 00:16.283
And did you tell him that you made
the same promise to Alex?

00:16.308 --> 00:17.344
No, I didn't.

00:17.434 --> 00:18.828
You wanna take me on,
you go for it,

00:18.852 --> 00:19.954
'cause I didn't get
where I am

00:19.978 --> 00:21.206
by letting people like you
push me around.

00:21.230 --> 00:23.973
David Fox wants a fight,
and I'm gonna give him one.

00:24.066 --> 00:25.102
A fight about what?

00:25.192 --> 00:27.400
He doesn't want to pay
our cleaning woman overtime.

00:27.486 --> 00:28.588
Harvey, this isn't what we do.

00:28.612 --> 00:30.173
- Mike would have done it.
- And Mike's not here anymore

00:30.197 --> 00:31.966
because he finally came
to terms with the fact

00:31.990 --> 00:33.071
that this isn't what we do.

00:33.158 --> 00:34.511
I'm not gonna let us start
losing clients

00:34.535 --> 00:36.596
because you decided
the cleaning staff is more important

00:36.620 --> 00:37.861
than the needs
of this firm.

00:37.955 --> 00:39.036
I didn't do anything

00:39.122 --> 00:40.892
- that you didn't sign off on.
- That's enough.

00:40.916 --> 00:42.519
You don't go to war
with the guy that owns your house

00:42.543 --> 00:45.206
over something like this.
End it, and end it today.

00:45.295 --> 00:47.662
I wanna make
a perfect baby with you.

00:47.756 --> 00:49.543
- Are you sure?
- Absolutely.

00:49.633 --> 00:51.420
And I don't want
to just pull the goalie.

00:51.510 --> 00:54.173
I want to start trying,
and I want to start trying right now.

00:54.263 --> 00:56.346
Remember that you told me
you promised Samantha

00:56.473 --> 00:58.009
- her name would go up next?
- I did.

00:58.100 --> 00:59.466
I made Alex the same promise.

00:59.560 --> 01:01.643
Then I guess there's
only one thing to do.

01:01.728 --> 01:03.014
Kick the can
down the road.

01:03.105 --> 01:04.596
I know you think
we're in competition

01:04.690 --> 01:06.352
for the same thing,
but we're not.

01:06.441 --> 01:07.932
Robert Zane
made me a promise.

01:08.902 --> 01:10.742
The next name that goes up
on the wall is mine.

01:13.657 --> 01:15.614
Bunny rabbit
goes around the tree once,

01:16.910 --> 01:19.152
bunny rabbit goes around
the tree twice...

01:19.746 --> 01:22.784
And I say bunny rabbit,
bunny rabbit, wanna play nice?

01:22.916 --> 01:25.704
- Sheila, what are you doing?
- I'm hunting "wabbits."

01:26.003 --> 01:27.790
No, no, no. Not Fudd.

01:28.297 --> 01:30.004
You know I can't resist
Elmer Fudd.

01:30.090 --> 01:31.126
Why would you want to?

01:31.216 --> 01:33.799
Oh, my God, Shelia,
I cannot right now.

01:33.885 --> 01:35.092
Why not?

01:35.178 --> 01:37.090
Because I have
a client meeting,

01:37.180 --> 01:39.046
and it's not just me.
Zane's coming too.

01:39.141 --> 01:42.100
So whatever you had in mind,
it's going to have to wait.

01:42.185 --> 01:43.551
All right.

01:43.645 --> 01:45.682
I didn't have
to do this, but...

01:47.232 --> 01:48.348
I'm fertile,

01:49.318 --> 01:52.186
and I am ripe
for the picking.

01:53.447 --> 01:55.860
So I don't care whether
you have a meeting or not.

01:55.949 --> 01:58.316
I'm going to need
your Johnny Appleseed.

01:59.786 --> 02:01.389
Sheila, you know if there's
one thing that revs me up

02:01.413 --> 02:03.057
more than Elmer Fudd,
it's American folk heroes.

02:03.081 --> 02:04.350
