- I would.

02:10.422 --> 02:12.400
Because it's time for John Henry to swing
the mighty hammer.

02:18.347 --> 02:19.633
Did you know?

02:21.016 --> 02:23.008
- Know what?
- That Zane promised Samantha

02:23.101 --> 02:24.245
she was the next
name partner.

02:24.269 --> 02:25.851
Alex, let's go
back up to my office.

02:25.937 --> 02:27.257
Sounds like you could use
a drink.

02:27.314 --> 02:30.557
What I could use is some goddamn honesty.
Did you know?

02:31.443 --> 02:32.479
Yeah, I knew.

02:32.569 --> 02:34.060
Then why the hell
didn't you tell me?

02:34.154 --> 02:35.914
Because no one's deciding
anything right now,

02:35.947 --> 02:37.634
and I didn't want
to upset you for no reason.

02:37.658 --> 02:39.298
No reason? Zane promised
his right hand...

02:39.326 --> 02:40.442
I know
what he promised.

02:40.535 --> 02:42.868
But look, you got me
and you got Louis.

02:42.954 --> 02:44.411
That's two against one.

02:44.498 --> 02:46.017
When the time is right,
we'll out-vote him.

02:46.041 --> 02:47.852
And when exactly
is the time going to be right?

02:47.876 --> 02:49.617
Six months?
A year? Three years?

02:49.753 --> 02:51.369
- Alex...
- No, Harvey, I want to know

02:51.463 --> 02:52.607
