would you sit tight?

03:02.140 --> 03:03.256
It may not be easy,

03:03.350 --> 03:04.886
- but, yeah, I would.
- That's funny.

03:04.976 --> 03:06.816
Because I recall you were
in a similar position

03:06.895 --> 03:08.056
