any younger,

03:43.640 --> 03:45.743
and we're just trying to take advantage
of any opportunity we can.

03:45.767 --> 03:46.803
<i>Why didn't you say so?</i>

03:46.893 --> 03:48.429
Just get here
as fast as you can.

03:48.520 --> 03:50.227
