you've used

09:50.090 --> 09:51.609
every tactic in the book
to force them to sell.

09:51.633 --> 09:53.793
Now you're looking to try some
that aren't in the book.

09:53.843 --> 09:55.630
Let's just say
that of the 15 companies

09:55.720 --> 09:58.007
that specialize in financing
that industry,

09:58.098 --> 10:01.637
