out of the CrytoGen business.

10:01.726 --> 10:03.638
And isn't it the strangest
coincidence

10:03.728 --> 10:06.596
that the 15th just so happens to be
one of our clients?

10:06.689 --> 10:08.555
The Lord works
in mysterious ways.

10:08.650 --> 10:11.170
