it's going to take

10:25.208 --> 10:26.574
to get our business.

10:26.668 --> 10:27.770
Alex, why don't we
listen to...

10:27.794 --> 10:29.647
No, Harvey, I'm not looking
to cross the line for these guys,

10:29.671 --> 10:30.773
and I don't care
if they tell me

10:30.797 --> 10:32.608
